      "main_description_html": "<ul class=\"contains-task-list\">\n<li class=\"task-list-item\"><input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"\" disabled=\"\" class=\"task-list-item-checkbox\" aria-label=\"Completed task\" checked=\"\"> App Store</li>\n<li class=\"task-list-item\"><input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"\" disabled=\"\" class=\"task-list-item-checkbox\" aria-label=\"Completed task\" checked=\"\"> Play Store</li>\n</ul>\n<markdown-accessiblity-table><table role=\"table\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Shot #</th>\n<th>Screen</th>\n<th>What to show</th>\n<th>Tips</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>1</td>\n<td><strong>Hero — Little Planet</strong></td>\n<td>Full-screen Little Planet projection</td>\n<td>Use the test panorama. Make sure the sphere is centered and visually striking. Hide the UI controls (tap to toggle).</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>2</td>\n<td><strong>Three projections</strong></td>\n<td>Normal / Little Planet / Fisheye of the same panorama</td>\n<td>Show all 3 modes — either side-by-side in a composite or as a 3-screenshot sequence.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3</td>\n<td><strong>Gallery</strong></td>\n<td>Dated grid of panorama thumbnails</td>\n<td>Populate the device with several good panoramas so the grid looks full. GoThru logo should be visible in the header.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>4</td>\n<td><strong>Capture</strong></td>\n<td>AR target grid mid-shoot</td>\n<td>Start a capture session, complete a few orange dots, then screenshot mid-shoot so the guidance grid is visible.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>5</td>\n<td><strong>Map</strong></td>\n<td>Map view with panorama pins</td>\n<td>Make sure several panoramas have GPS data so pins appear on the map. Zoom to a cluster.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>6</td>\n<td><strong>Send to Friend</strong></td>\n<td>QR code pairing or transfer progress</td>\n<td>Open Send to Friend on the sending device, screenshot the QR code screen.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table></markdown-accessiblity-table>\n<hr>\n<h2 dir=\"auto\">RESULT</h2>\n<p dir=\"auto\"><a 